io.orchestrate.client

Class TimeSeriesAggregateResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.orchestrate.client.AggregateResult
      • io.orchestrate.client.TimeSeriesAggregateResult

  • public class TimeSeriesAggregateResult
extends AggregateResult
    This class represents the results of a TimeSeriesAggregate function. The list of TimeSeriesBucket objects included with this aggregate indicate how many date values in the designated database field were found within each interval.
